          "process_md": "**Step 01:** The interested student needs to visit the [official website](https://apdascac.ap.gov.in/). \n**Step 02:** Click on the &quot;Online Applications&quot; on the home page. \n**Step 03:** Select the category &quot;click here to apply for differently abled schemes&quot; \n**Step 04:** Now click on &quot;Apply Online&quot; respect to the scheme name.\n**Step 05:** And confirm your registration. \n<br>\n\n> **If applicant was not register earlier**\n\n**Step 06:** Answer the above registration question as &quot;No&quot;. \n**Step 07:** Fill in your Aadhaar card name, Aadhaar number, Mobile number, email ID.\n**Step 08:** Create a new password for this application.\n**Step 09:** Click on &quot;Register&quot; After that get the registration number.\n<br>\n\n> **After the registration**\n\n**Step 10:** Click here to Login.\n**Step 11:** Again, ask the same &quot;Are you registered already: Yes/No Select &quot;Yes&quot;.\n**Step 12:** Enter email/mobile number and password.\n**Step 13:** Click on &quot;Login&quot; and select the category again &quot;click here to apply for differently abled schemes&quot; .\n**Step 14:** Fill out the application form for personal employment and disability detail.\n**Step 15:** Click on &quot;Submit&quot;.\n<br>\n\n"
        }
